Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:31.40,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\1a&HFF&\blur8}漕いで行く　漕いで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:33.74,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\1a&HFF&\blur8}どこへ行こう
